700
00:47:31,120 --> 00:47:32,280
Ne!

701
00:47:32,360 --> 00:47:34,880
Da.I sad je najveci svetac
za kuvare.

702
00:47:36,400 --> 00:47:38,240
Mislim da ako se pomolite sa njim,

703
00:47:38,240 --> 00:47:40,720
on ce vam pomoci
oko kuvanja za nekoga.

704
00:47:41,680 --> 00:47:43,800
Hvala vam, Signor Martini.

705
00:47:53,000 --> 00:47:54,320
Cestit Boic, Signora.

706
00:47:54,440 --> 00:47:56,440
Cestit Boic.

707
00:48:13,440 --> 00:48:16,800
Mo molitve za San Lorenza
su urodile plodom.

708
00:48:16,800 --> 00:48:20,440
Shvatila sam da vec
imam za koga da kuvam.

709
00:48:21,400 --> 00:48:23,120
Za mnogo njih.

710
00:49:23,440 --> 00:49:24,880
Bravo!
- Ahh!

711
00:49:27,560 --> 00:49:28,600
Bravo!
- Bravo!

712
00:49:37,720 --> 00:49:40,800
Boe.
- Vidiš, Frances? Italijanski je lak.

713
00:49:47,200 --> 00:49:48,160
Ne!

714
00:50:06,400 --> 00:50:08,320
Jesi li pricao sa njom?

715
00:50:10,920 --> 00:50:12,240
Da.

716
00:50:13,000 --> 00:50:14,560
Pricao sam sa njom.

717
00:50:14,640 --> 00:50:17,240
Zašto ne sedneš pored
nje? Hajde.

718
00:50:17,320 --> 00:50:18,760
Ok.

719
00:50:41,680 --> 00:50:43,520
Katherine!

720
00:50:46,200 --> 00:50:48,120
Francesca!
Dodi gore!

721
00:50:48,120 --> 00:50:49,920
Slikam moj portret.

722
00:50:51,960 --> 00:50:53,200
Katherine?

723
00:50:53,280 --> 00:50:55,520
Dodi.
Ovde sam.

724
00:51:10,000 --> 00:51:13,800
Mislim da cu doci drugi put.
- Zašto? Nesmetaš mi ti.

725
00:51:13,920 --> 00:51:17,560
Frances, ovo je Zeus.

726
00:51:17,560 --> 00:51:19,560
On je student umetnosti
iz Makedonije.

727
00:51:19,680 --> 00:51:22,920
Kod mene je dok proucava
Toskansko svetlo.

728
00:51:23,040 --> 00:51:24,960
Još vina, dragi.

729
00:51:32,320 --> 00:51:34,720
Nije loš.

730
00:51:34,840 --> 00:51:36,640
A nije ni dobar.

731
00:51:38,840 --> 00:51:42,400
Slušaj, ja idem,
ali cu se navratiti drugi put.

732
00:51:42,480 --> 00:51:44,800
Oh, tako si dosadna!

733
00:51:44,880 --> 00:51:45,640
Šta?

734
00:51:45,760 --> 00:51:47,200
I said you're boring.

735
00:51:47,280 --> 00:51:49,320
Pogledaj se!

736
00:51:49,400 --> 00:51:50,560
Nesrecna si opet.

737
00:51:50,640 --> 00:51:52,200
Opet!

738
00:51:52,280 --> 00:51:55,840
Ti sa kao velika crna rupa.

739
00:51:55,920 --> 00:51:57,280
Izvini,ali ja...

740
00:51:57,360 --> 00:52:01,480
Fefe je uvek govorio,
'Tuga je trošenje vremena.

741
00:52:01,480 --> 00:52:05,400
To je prošlost koja te pravi
bogaljem u sadašnjici. '

742
00:52:05,520 --> 00:52:07,040
Tek sam došla.
Samo što sam prošla kroz vrata.

743
00:52:07,160 --> 00:52:11,560
Kako ceš ikada biti srecna
ako nastaviš da se koprcaš?

744
00:52:11,560 --> 00:52:15,000
Slušaj,
kada sam bila mala,

745
00:52:15,120 --> 00:52:17,480
Nekada sam provodila sate
traeci ensku bubu.

746
00:52:17,480 --> 00:52:21,440
Na kraju, sam odustala
i zaspala na travi.

747
00:52:21,520 --> 00:52:25,280
Kada sam se probudila,
one su hodale po meni.

748
00:52:26,240 --> 00:52:27,560
Pa?

749
00:52:27,680 --> 00:52:32,360
Pa idi radi na tvojoj kuci
i zaboravi na to.

750
00:52:32,360 --> 00:52:34,200
Rekla sam idi!

751
00:52:34,280 --> 00:52:36,400
Idem!

752
00:52:40,440 --> 00:52:43,120
Radi na tvojoj kuci
i zaboravi na to.

753
00:52:44,840 --> 00:52:47,240
Gospode,zašto se ja nisam
setila toga?

754
00:52:48,400 --> 00:52:51,160
Dode vreme u ivotu
svakog dekoratera.

755
00:52:51,240 --> 00:52:53,960
Kada ne ele više
korisne savete.

756
00:52:54,040 --> 00:52:57,120
Dode vreme kada ne eliš
više nepouzdane tipove

757
00:52:57,200 --> 00:52:59,120
koji gledaju u tebe
misleci bog zna šta,

758
00:52:59,200 --> 00:53:00,360
Da ti šapucu na Poljskom

759
00:53:00,480 --> 00:53:02,960
I stvarno ti je drago
što nerazumeš.

760
00:53:06,320 --> 00:53:09,280
I ti to nemoeš da podneseš
i dode vreme

761
00:53:09,400 --> 00:53:11,320
kada jednostavno moraš da izadeš.

762
00:53:46,320 --> 00:53:48,320
Signorina.

763
00:53:48,400 --> 00:53:49,680
Bella!

764
00:53:49,680 --> 00:53:50,920
Sjajno.

765
00:53:53,400 --> 00:53:55,040
Ma fenomenalni ste!

766
00:53:55,600 --> 00:53:57,320
Dovidenja!

767
00:54:09,040 --> 00:54:11,520
Vi ste Amerikanka?

768
00:54:11,520 --> 00:54:13,640
Englleskinja? Irkinja?

769
00:54:16,240 --> 00:54:18,240
Tu si.
Traim te svuda.

770
00:54:18,320 --> 00:54:19,480
Rekao si da ce mo se naci.

771
00:54:19,600 --> 00:54:22,280
Traim te vec 20 minuta.

772
00:54:22,360 --> 00:54:24,200
Ko ste vi?
- Izvinite.

773
00:54:24,280 --> 00:54:26,400
Mi scusi.
Hvala vam.

774
00:54:26,480 --> 00:54:28,880
Cekajte. Poljubili ste me
i sad idete?

775
00:54:29,000 --> 00:54:30,320
Da.

776
00:54:30,320 --> 00:54:32,040
Izvini.

777
00:54:33,760 --> 00:54:34,920
Uredu.

778
00:54:58,920 --> 00:55:00,240
Zakasnili ste.

779
00:55:00,360 --> 00:55:01,320
Molim?

780
00:55:01,400 --> 00:55:03,800
Vec sam našao drugu.

781
00:55:06,280 --> 00:55:07,840
Ja gubim.

782
00:55:09,760 --> 00:55:10,880
Pitala sam se,
moete li mi pomoci.

783
00:55:10,880 --> 00:55:12,440
Pokušavam da nadem antikvarnicu.

784
00:55:12,040 --> 00:55:14,840
Koja prodaje delove za lustere.

785
00:55:14,920 --> 00:55:16,560
Lustere.

786
00:55:16,640 --> 00:55:17,880
Vetre-ria.
- Vetreria.

787
00:55:18,000 --> 00:55:20,280
Vetreria, da.
- Uredu.

788
00:55:20,400 --> 00:55:22,680
Via di La Casanova.

789
00:55:22,800 --> 00:55:24,040
A da, Via di La Casanova.

790
00:55:24,120 --> 00:55:25,960
Da.
- Znate?

791
00:55:26,040 --> 00:55:26,920
Ne.

792
00:55:28,080 --> 00:55:30,280
Ali znam za drugu radnju.

793
00:55:30,360 --> 00:55:33,040
Moj rodak dri jednu.
- Vaš rodak dri vetreria?

794
00:55:33,160 --> 00:55:35,360
Da. Antikvitete.

795
00:55:35,360 --> 00:55:36,400
Je li daleko?

796
00:55:36,400 --> 00:55:37,920
Na oko 3 sata.

797
00:55:38,040 --> 00:55:40,640
2 ako vozim brzo.

798
00:55:40,640 --> 00:55:41,400
2 sata?

799
00:55:41,400 --> 00:55:48,120
Uredu. Jedan ako vozim,
stvarno, stvarno brzo.

800
00:55:48,200 --> 00:55:52,520
To je lepo, ali hvala.
Ne.

801
00:55:52,520 --> 00:55:57,200
Vi verovatno mislite da pokušavam
da vas smotam.

802
00:55:57,320 --> 00:55:59,440
Smotate?

803
00:55:59,520 --> 00:56:02,880
Smuvate.

804
00:56:02,960 --> 00:56:04,320
Da.
Tu lei zec.

805
00:56:04,400 --> 00:56:08,240
Ali vi ste ta koja me je zgrabila
pretvarajuci se da sam vam mu.

806
00:56:08,360 --> 00:56:10,560
Vi ste verovatno jednao od
onih ludih Amerikanki

807
00:56:10,640 --> 00:56:14,280
kao naprimer 'Carlijevi andeli, '
i onda ce te mi baciti neki kun-fu potez

